# Skill add: vendor an upstream skill into the Commons — pinned at a commit, validated, scanned, PR'd.
Output docs/demos/gif/13-skill-add.gif
Output docs/demos/mp4/13-skill-add.mp4
Source docs/demos/tapes/lib/style.tape
Source docs/demos/tapes/lib/world.tape

Type "# adopt a skill for the whole team — pinned at the upstream commit"
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 500ms

Type@30ms "roboto-mem skill add file:///tmp/roboto-mem-demo/skills.git --author ada"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 6s
